# Bucket List Service API

BLiSA is a simple API allowing users to _CREATE bucketlists_ and _items_ in them. Then they are able to _VIEW_, _UPDATE_ and _DELETE_ them.

## User Authentification [/auth/login/]

### Logs a user in [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "us3rn@m3",
            "password": "p@ssw0rd"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "token": "t0k3n"
        }

